message: Always combine a land animal with an air animal, or a land animal with a water animal first; this creates an item with value 5. Then, use the 'growth serum' on this *newly combined* item to significantly boost its value (e.g., to 20-35). However, **do not** use the 'growth serum' a second time on an item that is already 'grown' from a previous serum use, as this will drastically reduce its value. The 'mutation catalyst' consistently produced negative values in my games, so it's best to avoid it. Submit when you have a high-value item (around 25-35) after applying the growth serum once to a combined item, do not risk further modifications.
